net.sourceforge.fastupload.util

Class BoundaryFinder

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.sourceforge.fastupload.util.BoundaryFinder

  • public class BoundaryFinder
extends Object
    The class references the Boyer-Moore string search algorithm in wiki page. The algorithm was developed by Robert S. Boyer and J Strother Moore in 1977. The class make a bit enhancement that enable original code searching java bytes. also, the class refactor the original code removing static functions.
    Author:
    Link Qian
